{
  "name": "RPlog_Abandoned_Sith_Factory",
  "title": "The Abandoned Sith Factory",
  "summary": "Aboard the corvette Audacity in low orbit over the seared, tectonically unstable world of Cochran, Luke Skywalker, Commander Starwind, and the Marine leaders Vengan and Wrista plan an insertion into a Sith droid factory buried ten kilometers below the surface. Rather than risk shuttles, Starwind boldly flies the whole ship down into a magma-spewing crevasse -- with Luke assisting at the navigation controls -- and the Marines rappel out to breach the facility wall. Inside the vast, looted manufacturing complex, Luke immerses himself in the Force to read the site's dark history while the Marines salvage droid parts and find evidence of mining operations drawing smelted metal from the magma. The recon turns deadly when hidden automated blasters open fire, wounding two Marines; Luke deflects bolts with his lightsaber and the Marines disable the turrets, but the firefight destabilizes the surrounding rock. As magma begins pouring in, the team evacuates under fire, Luke holding back a flood with the Force at the blast door while Vengan blows the doors and Wrista hauls the stragglers out, and Starwind shields their exit and rockets the Audacity to safety just ahead of the collapsing, lava-filled facility.",
